Fix client boot dying silently (root cause of everything being unclickable)

The real bug behind "can't upgrade / nav dead / income stuck at 0": a single
require/runtime error in ClientMain halted the entire client boot, so NO
controller initialised and the ProfileUpdated/ShowNotification handlers never
connected. Every dead symptom traced to this one point.

- ClientMain: isolate every require, init, and remote handler in pcall so one
  bad module can never take down the rest. Added boot diagnostics
  ("[StadiumTycoon] Client booting / initialised / ready") so the Output
  console shows exactly how far boot gets.
- StadiumController + PackOpenController: replace direct-index config requires
  (ReplicatedStorage.Config.X) with WaitForChild, so a slow-replicating Config
  on the client can't throw at require time.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
